		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="1" id="1">
			<answer correct="false">A.  hide any low expectations they may have of individual students.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="2" id="2">
			<answer correct="true">B.  create the appropriate atmosphere during the lesson.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="3" id="3">
			<answer correct="false">C.  reward students' efforts even when they fail.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="4" id="4">
			<answer correct="true">D.  tell students the reason for each exercise they do.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="5" id="5">
			<answer correct="false">E.  try to make learning fun.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="6" id="6">
			<answer correct="true">A.  are demanding but not impossible.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="7" id="7">
			<answer correct="false">B.  are extrinsically rewarding.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="8" id="8">
			<answer correct="false">C.  do not take too long.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="9" id="9">
			<answer correct="true">D.  are related to everyday life.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="10" id="10">
			<answer correct="false">E.  are not too tiring.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="11" id="11">
			<answer correct="false">A.  concentrate on their strengths rather than on their weaknesses.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="12" id="12">
			<answer correct="true">B.  understand the cause of their failure.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="13" id="13">
			<answer correct="false">C.  realise that their failure is not their fault.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="14" id="14">
			<answer correct="false">D.  concentrate in class.</answer>
		</field>
		<field mode="0" type="i:target" group="15" id="15">
			<answer correct="true">E.  change the way they do things.</answer>
		</field>
