		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+0" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000">Now read through the possible endings for each sentence. Note the ones which seem most likely or that you think you remember from earlier readings of the text.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
